        How a Rental Appraisal Affects the Sale Price of an Investment Property in Brisbane
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        A rental appraisal letter can strengthen your position as a seller, but only if you understand what it does and does not tell buyers. Here is what you need to know.
      </p>
